OL,3,CMan told to remove garden structure
OL,4,Chires crane to prove 'it's not a shed'
OL,6,FA man who has been ordered to remove a
OL,7,Fstructure in his garden by the council
OL,8,Fhas hired a crane to lift it off the
OL,9,Fground to show its moveability.
OL,11,FSteve Holden had applied to put a shed
OL,12,Fup outside his house in Hastings, but
OL,13,Fhe was turned down.
OL,15,FHe then found a builder who said he
OL,16,Fcould make it in a way it can be
OL,17,Ftreated as a caravan in planning terms
OL,18,Fand would not need council approval.
