OL,4,Chires crane to prove 'it's not a shed'
OL,6,FHe has now been served with an
OL,7,Fenforcement notice by Hastings Borough
OL,8,FCouncil to remove the structure.
OL,10,FHomeowner, Steve Holden said: "(The
OL,11,Fbuilder) assured me that he could
OL,12,Fbuild a moveable structure that didn't
OL,13,Frequire planning permission.
OL,15,F"I don't want to be in dispute with
OL,16,Fthe council, so I figured I'd got the
OL,17,Fright solution, but apparently not.
OL,19,F"The council eventually served me,
OL,20,Fafter a long process and a couple of
OL,21,Fappeals, with an enforcement notice.
