OL,3,CMan told to remove garden structure
OL,4,Chires crane to prove 'it's not a shed'
OL,6,F"We managed to lift it about 18 inches
OL,7,Foff the ground, show clear air
OL,8,Funderneath to show it's not attached
OL,9,Fto any foundation and it is indeed a
OL,10,Fmoveable structure."
OL,12,FThe builder says because the structure
OL,13,Fis moveable, it should be treated as a
OL,14,Fcaravan in planning terms.
OL,16,F"It's not a shed because there's
OL,17,Fnothing underneath, there's no
OL,18,Ffoundation," the structure's builder,
OL,19,FPeter Bucklitsch said.
