OL,3,CMan told to remove garden structure
OL,4,Chires crane to prove 'it's not a shed'
OL,6,F"The frame itself is a complete frame,
OL,7,Fit needs nothing under each leg."
OL,9,FIn a statement, Hastings Borough
OL,10,FCouncil said: "The Planning
OL,11,FEnforcement Team have, and continue to
OL,12,Fbe, open to discussion with Mr Holden
OL,13,Fregarding this matter, however the
OL,14,Fstructure is in breach of planning
OL,15,Fcontrol.
OL,17,F"Mr Holden has the right to appeal
OL,18,Fagainst the enforcement action taken
OL,19,Fby the Council, and he is able to make
OL,20,Fhis representations regarding the
OL,21,Fstructure to a planning inspector."
